{
  "title": "得到你的人却得不到你的心",
  "title_raw": "得到你的人却得不到你的心",
  "version": null,
  "artist": "邓涛",
  "group_key": "得到你的人却得不到你的心|邓涛",
  "writers": {
    "lyricist": "欢子",
    "composer": "欢子",
    "arranger": null
  },
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 31.81,
      "time_str": "00:31.810",
      "text": "你迷人的眼神俘虏了我的心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 36.19,
      "time_str": "00:36.190",
      "text": "我想没有什么东西比这更致命",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.25,
      "time_str": "00:40.250",
      "text": "我努力想结束这段迷失的感情",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.74,
      "time_str": "00:44.740",
      "text": "可我发现没有勇气和你说再见",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 48.45,
      "time_str": "00:48.450",
      "text": "难到注定爱上你最后伤的是自己",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 52.76,
      "time_str": "00:52.760",
      "text": "难道注定这一切将是回忆",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.01,
      "time_str": "00:57.010",
      "text": "你的心不属于我为何和我在一起",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 61.38,
      "time_str": "01:01.380",
      "text": "是不是因为寂寞和空虚",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 67.57,
      "time_str": "01:07.570",
      "text": "如果我得到你的人却得不到你的心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 72.57,
      "time_str": "01:12.570",
      "text": "就算得到全世界也不开心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 76.55,
      "time_str": "01:16.550",
      "text": "我想问一问你能否爱我一次",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 81.13,
      "time_str": "01:21.130",
      "text": "遗憾我并不是你唯一",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 84.75,
      "time_str": "01:24.750",
      "text": "如果我失去这一切能换来你的真心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 89.63,
      "time_str": "01:29.630",
      "text": "就算失去全世界也不伤心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 93.75,
      "time_str": "01:33.750",
      "text": "我以为人一起心就会在一起",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 98.19,
      "time_str": "01:38.190",
      "text": "可怜我还一直为你钟情",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
